        <td>Low</td>
        <td>Small spaces, kitchens, and apartment gardeners</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Lettuce or radish containers</td>
        <td>Low to moderate</td>
        <td>Cool spring or fall growing</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>One raised bed of mixed greens and herbs</td>
        <td>Moderate</td>
        <td>Beginners with outdoor space</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Cherry tomato in a container</td>
        <td>Moderate</td>
        <td>Sunny patios with enough warm weather</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
